{"tid":431534,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(復仇向web小說既清泉)討厭第四次死屬性魔術師","createTime":"2017-10-10T20:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T16:53:53.000Z","uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbd09cd74e079421150491d716ab75f1164d2b2","tid":431534,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T20:25:57.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到web11話 冇撚得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故事：男主同一百位同學因意外死亡  <br />\n轉生前因為個神諗住補償呢班學生但因為一個失誤淨係冇施予正面既恩賜比男主.得一堆負面能力..累到男主第二次轉生因為黑仔比人賣去研究再意外慘死..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男主既能力係死靈魔術<br />\n好睇在男主自己本身就係廢既<br />\n然後點樣運用呢堆負面能力去營運自己既兵力<br />\n<br />\n講到復仇部份 (因為自己第三次轉生既老母比人害死)<br />\n係行理智有遠見方式咁去諗點樣對付人地<br />\n呢一part係頭8話已經睇到男主點樣深謀遠慮<br />\n會分析點樣點樣做會令到對家點樣得到壞處<br />\n比起亂咁虐殺屠殺 更加佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d6a04d32d913eed256079445c8a5dca9185eca","tid":431534,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T20:27:48.000Z","msg":"仲有 我未見過咁仆街既神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遲早比人郁"},{"pid":"f959deeb19284d30b90d279dbd217185fd82c9fd","tid":431534,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T23:15:10.000Z","msg":"呢套有睇熟肉<br />\n去到中期都係建國Sim city<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有幾個勢力係幾好睇既"},{"pid":"2bb21e1f1f0160371c9ab552f1767806ca874fe9","tid":431534,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T23:29:40.000Z","msg":"樓主又推伏作"},{"pid":"260bd5feccfe23c598318bd173c12565f16731df","tid":431534,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套有睇熟肉<br />\n去到中期都係建國Sim city<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有幾個勢力係幾好睇既</blockquote><br />\n呢套野 比我既感覺係<br />\n好多位都解釋得好到位而又唔覺得煩覆<br />\n不過睇佢點樣部署真係幾好睇"},{"pid":"1d11239c0711791d985f94d46badbd133cb67ad7","tid":431534,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主又推伏作</blockquote><br />\n真心不騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為同時揀左幾套黎睇 <br />\n得呢套睇落去見得下人"},{"pid":"6c3b484c9c61cd8d4bd36efe78025eadcdb7a9f6","tid":431534,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"個故事同平凡職業好似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3126940844cd32efdee03189f83ec0371f8120f3","tid":431534,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個故事同平凡職業好似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平凡職業我都有睇過下小說第一卷到鬆d<br />\n比較偏向「女」果一方面 嫌套路左小小<br />\n依家我睇緊呢套 感覺偏向運營自己部隊既feel <br />\n就開頭黎睇都差好遠...復仇得黎唔會用太俗既方法"},{"pid":"a98966f80dc68e16f76abedddc19df12ab037f84","tid":431534,"uid":95074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"睇到後面就會發現佢又係成日話自己廢但一出黎打就屈曬機果堆黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295bb54f468dbd2579d64176a6c41d628b1d16b1","tid":431534,"uid":115525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個故事同平凡職業好似喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平凡職業我都有睇過下小說第一卷到鬆d<br />\n比較偏向「女」果一方面 嫌套路左小小<br />\n依家我睇緊呢套 感覺偏向運營自己部隊既feel <br />\n就開頭黎睇都差好遠...復仇得黎唔會用太俗既方法</blockquote><br />\n同平凡職業差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd175e13324705ba03bc5c77486e94bb3541c45c","tid":4315